1. Vlada je donela novi zakon. (*vlada*) (The government has passed a new law.)
2. Vladu je formirala koalicija. (koalicija *vladu*) (The coalition formed the government.)
3. Oni su protiv vladine politike. (protiv *vladine*) (They are against the government's policy.)
4. Vladajuća stranka ima većinu u parlamentu. (*vladajuća*) (The ruling party has a majority in parliament.)
5. Ustav ograničava moć vlasti. (moć *vlasti*) (The constitution limits the power of the authorities.)
6. Opozicija kritikuje vladu zbog korupcije. (zbog *vlade*) (The opposition criticizes the government for corruption.)
7. U vreme pandemije, vlada je donela oštre mere. (*vlada*) (During the pandemic, the government has implemented strict measures.)
8. Nije lako vladati u ovako teškim vremenima. (*vladati*) (It's not easy to govern in such difficult times.)
9. Vladari su se sukobili oko teritorije. (*vladari*) (The rulers have clashed over territory.)
10. Mnogi građani žele da promene vlast. (promene *vlasti*) (Many citizens want to change the government.)